System
  Display system info
    inxi - Fxz
    lshw
    lscpu
  Storage
    lsblk
    blkid

Networking
    nmcli
  IP
    ip addr ~ show ip address
  DNS
    nslookup <domain name>
    dig <domain name>
    systemd-resolve --status

Users/Groups
    > adduser ~ interactive add user account
    > usermod -aG groupname user ~ adds 'user' to the 'groupname' group
    > less /etc/group ~ view all groups
    > groups ~ lists all groups the user belongs to
    > id [user] ~ similar to groups
    > sudo groupadd groupname ~ adds group 'groupname'
    > newgrp groupname ~ applies changes to group 'groupname' without having to logout/in

DNS
    > sudo systemd-resolve --flush-cache
    > sudo systemd-resolve --statistics
